text: Polyrhaphis papulosa is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Olivier in 1795. It is known from Colombia, Peru, Brazil, and French Guiana.BioLib.cz - Polyrhaphis papulosa. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1795
